Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,def2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCH
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,def2,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They call it the\N``National Liberation Army.''
